==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Damewort
<hw>Dame"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
cruciferous plant (<spn>Hesperis matronalis</spn>), remarkable for its
fragrance, especially toward the close of the day; -- called also
<altname>rocket</altname> and <altname>dame's violet</altname>.</def>
<rj><au>Loudon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Damiana</ent>⟦br⟧
